=== HOLOGRAPHIC_MAZE ===
# id: 57
# title: The Holographic Maze
# chinese_title: 全息迷宫
# category: Puzzle
# mode: dungeon

Hard-light projectors create a maze that fills the cargo bay. The walls shift every thirty seconds, rearranging the path. Characters flash on each wall segment, and you notice that walls marked with the same radical family never block each other.

* [Follow walls with matching radicals]
  ~ gain_radical("又")
  "迷" (mí) — lost, maze, confused. The radical "又" relates to repetition.
* [Map the pattern between shifts]
  ~ gain_xp(25)
  "图" (tú) — map, diagram
* [Wait for the projectors to cycle off]
  ~ gain_xp(10)
  "等" (děng) — to wait
* [Sprint through before walls shift]
  ~ damage(5)
  "急" (jí) — hurried, urgent
